  <abstract id="abstr_chi" date-changed="20091229" lang="chi" format="original">
    <p num="1">本实用新型提供了一种具有语言功能的电机智检控制器，包括接触器D、电流互感器E、应答器F、接收器G及遥控器H，应答器F根据接收器G及与其相对应的遥控器H所发出的指令，给放大处理后逐使接触器D的通断来控制电机M的开停，再经电流互感器E采集电机M工作的各种状态加以智能检测，并通过语言方式表达出来，彻底解决了长期靠人工观察指示灯、仪表检测方式的弊端，是一项值得推广的技术。</p>
  </abstract>
  <abstract id="abstr_eng" date-changed="20091229" lang="eng" format="original">
    <p>The utility model provides an intelligent testing and controlling device with a speech function, which comprising a contactor D, a current mutual inductor E, a responder F, an acceptor G and a remote controller H. According to the instruction generated by the acceptor G and the corresponding remote controller H, the responder F controls the starting and stopping of the motor M by the on and off of the contactor D after amplifying process and then intelligently checks various working attitudes of the motor M collecting by the current mutual inductor E for expression in a language mode. The utility model which thoroughly solves the disadvantages of artificially observing indicating lamp and instrument detection in a long time is a technique which is worth popularized.</p>
  </abstract>
